Enum FileIoProvider.OPERATION

    org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.server.datanode.FileIoProvider

    public static enum FileIoProvider.OPERATION
extends Enum<FileIoProvider.OPERATION>
    Lists the types of file system operations. Passed to the IO hooks so implementations can choose behavior based on specific operations.
